[size=14pt][font=georgia]I like a good server where I can log in and then lay my dick on my keyboard then flop it around a lot and see how far I get. This server seems to be the best one for that, and I’m pleased that the developers have compensated for people like me, thanks Youthix. I needed this kind of server to fit my odd lifestyle and you happened to do it perfectly. You claim to have the best RSPS experience, and I can agree with this 100%! 5 dick flops out of 5![/font][/size]
